What's he celebrating?

01:44:21.046 --> 01:44:23.673
I don't know.

01:44:23.757 --> 01:44:25.841
I think he just
wanna go out
on top.

01:45:43.170 --> 01:45:44.587
Go! Go!

01:45:50.677 --> 01:45:52.303
That's it.

01:46:04.024 --> 01:46:05.191
